    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error achieves level 3 against a level 2 requirement, providing additional confidence. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 per the MRL 2 framework and are satisfied by existing SQA and verification activities. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is directly supported by the validated CFD outputs. The credibility assessment team concludes that the model has sufficient credibility to support the COU decision for the Class II CPB device.",
